repos_data.description: DataSphereStudio is a one stop data application development& management portal, covering scenarios including data exchange, desensitization/cleansing, analysis/mining, quality measurement, visualization, and task scheduling.
Shell wrapper for OpenAI's ChatGPT, DALL-E, Whisper, and TTS. Features LocalAI, Ollama, Gemini, Mistral, Groq, and Anthropic integration.
